{"tid":440245,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"淫邪台軍副營長邊摸女兵下體邊問「好想要吧？」","createTime":"2017-10-18T14:45:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T01:56:01.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2aba53969b4ee231ddaae15f7596db8401191732","tid":440245,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T14:45:02.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">陸軍砲兵一名少校副營長2015年間以督導業務為由，2度在車內分別摳摸女兵下體和胸部，甚至大膽問女兵「妳想要嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？」女兵雖感到不舒服，但因害怕不敢反抗，事後找部隊裡的學姊訴苦，才鼓起勇氣向上級回報，揭發副營長淫行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imagelab.nownews.com/?w=1080&amp;q=85&amp;src=https://img.nownews.com/nownews_production/images/5992a66dea2b7b14dfd91194_201708151544.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimagelab.nownews.com%2F%3Fw%3D1080%26q%3D85%26src%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.nownews.com%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F5992a66dea2b7b14dfd91194_201708151544.jpg&h=94eba9a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲色副營長秒變狼，摳摸女兵下體還問「想要嗎？」（示意圖／NOWnews資料照）</span><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nownews.com/news/20171012/2623625\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F20171012%2F2623625&d=eHgTl0akRFSu%2Bkp8QTI6luPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=43460a77\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nownews.com/news/20171012/2623625</a></div>"},{"pid":"7ba1c0e5ec1b998bdf6918bc520652f42b79f5d8","tid":440245,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T14:47:05.000Z","msg":"據了解，女兵當時剛滿20歲、入伍1年多，在砲兵營擔任彈藥兵，而涉案的副營長則督導相關後勤業務。2015年11月2日，副營長指派女兵一同開車前往桃園彈藥庫清點彈藥，過程中卻在車上解開女兵褲袋、強脫內衣，伸出狼爪撫摸胸部和下體，猥褻時間長達5分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n事後，副營長見女兵不敢吭聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，隔天竟得寸進尺再要求女兵陪同前往彈藥庫，這次他更大膽的搓揉女兵胸部並摳摸下體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，甚至直接問「妳想要嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？」女兵當場嚇呆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但又因為心裡害怕不敢反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，最後在學姊的鼓勵下，才向營隊副連長說出實情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n女兵表示，起初副營長表示要在車上午睡，卻突然靠向副駕駛座並伸手強脫女兵衣褲，更對她又摸又親，原以為第二天副營長應該不敢在犯，怎料卻仍再度被猥褻。而副營長則辯稱，2人是男女交往關係，愛撫過程中女兵也沒有拒絕，更表示「可不可以不要那麼早回營區」，且女兵在工作結束後還主動跟上來，也沒見她當下向上級求助，否認性侵。<br />\n<br />\n由於雙方事發前不熟也沒私交，法官不採信副營長辯詞，認定他確實是利用要求絕對階級與職務服從之便，對女兵猥褻得逞。雖副營長惡行敗壞軍紀，但2人私下達成和解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，一審依2個利用權勢猥褻罪合併判處副營長5月徒刑、得易科罰金15萬元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，經上訴，高等法院維持一審判決，可上訴。"},{"pid":"8736c572e9d9df3c73907176108df8b623bbc122","tid":440245,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T23:26:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77670a65c0ff401b8b57dd9d75a38f4a4d708a96","tid":440245,"uid":60028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T01:10:36.000Z","msg":"在炮兵營擔任彈藥兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6841b0d88b0709f2127e8c9da21266e9356af3e6","tid":440245,"uid":84212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T01:56:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}